The paper discusses the use of reinforcement learning to automate the process of predictive modeling, which falls under the category of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of various techniques such as data imputation, feature transformations, and hyper-parameter search, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the role of experienced data scientists in the modeling process, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and computational engineering (cs.CE).
